## Slide 4 — Human Oversight Where It Counts

DBAI is not autonomous. Every consequential decision has a human approval gate.

| Gate | Approver | What They See |
|---|---|---|
| Triage verdict | Dev Lead | AI severity + root cause + confidence score |
| Defect scope | Dev Lead | Acceptance criteria, affected components |
| Fix candidate | Developer | Code diff + AI rationale + risk flags |
| Test results | Dev / QA | Pass/fail + coverage delta |
| Deploy | Release Owner | Final sign-off with blast-radius summary |

Engineers stay in control. AI eliminates the paperwork between the decisions.

