## Slide 6 — Metrics You Can Show Upward

Once the pipeline is live, these are trackable without extra instrumentation:

- **MTTR** — Mean Time To Resolution, per defect category
- **Triage-to-Jira latency** — time from SNow Problem to developer-ready Defect
- **Developer ramp time** — time from Jira assignment to first commit
- **SNow SLA compliance rate** — % of Problems closed before breach
- **Escaped defect rate** — defects that regress after first fix
- **AI acceptance rate** — how often triage verdicts and fix suggestions are approved unchanged

